                "content": "Don't implement insert_before. All we need is insert_after with the file start token. Specify the pytest syntax using something resembling a standard grammar and then we'll make sure we support exactly that. Be sure to keep the same pattern as the other tools, handling all errors and returning them, sending helpful error messages, dedenting or cleaning the code, etc.",
