                                                                                                                                                         {
                                                                                                                                                          "content": "This confirms our problem: we're losing all comments and non-AST elements because we're working purely with the AST. When we parse and reconstruct the source, we lose:\n1. Comments (both inline and standalone)\n2. Exact whitespace/indentation\n3. Original line formatting\n\nWe need to modify `_handle_insertion` to work with the raw source lines instead of AST when doing line-based insertion. Let me fix this in the ScopeTransformer:",
