                                          "node_class": "AnthropicNode",
                                          "replies": [
                                           {
                                            "content": "Note that in item 3.1, we may only be losing the \" part of the comment by replacing it with a '. I think that's the default to_source behavior. Would you review the old tool and how it approached these problems? I believe we just accepted some of these difficulties (but maybe the improved tool should not). What would you recommend to preserve these things? Some kind of special tokens to tag in and out specific text?",
                                            "pending_results": [],
