                                              "node_class": "AnthropicNode",
                                              "replies": [
                                               {
                                                "content": "Not a fan of the token-based approach, eh? I believe we started with a full sourcemapper but ran into a lot of issues and edge cases. Is there a reason you prefer that approach to tokens?",
