                                                                                                          "content": "I see several issues with the tokenization implementation:\n\n1. The tokenization itself isn't working correctly - our tokens are malformed:\n```python\n;TOKEN__1b0d354e_0=;TOKEN__1b0d354e_6='''';;  # This is not valid Python\n```\n\nWe need to fix the token format to be:\n```python\n;TOKEN__1b0d354e_0='content';  # Valid Python assignment\n```\n\n2. We're getting recursive tokenization - tokens within tokens, which is causing the SyntaxError.\n\nLet me fix the tokenize_source function first:",
