                                                                                                              "content": "\n        Error: Could not find match. Best potential match: 326\n        Context:\n        [\"324:     comment_pattern = '([^#]*)(#[^\\\\\\\\n]*)'\", '325:     for match in re.finditer(comment_pattern, tokenized):', '326:         code, comment = match.groups()', '327:         if not code.strip():', '328:             continue']\n        Match quality: 0.79"
